Su Ruo's death was just an accident.

9
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,400
Stop getting involved for no reason.

10
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:54,680
If he has nothing to hide,

11
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,640
