19
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,240
He showed up again last night.

20
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,640
That's quite a coincidence.

21
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:10,600
It is a coincidence.

22
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,320
That's why we're investigating.

23
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:13,760
So, how's it going?

24
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,360
Did you check last night's footage?

25
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,440
