35
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,480
I don't know where he lives now,

36
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:36,160
but fifteen years ago

37
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:40,360
he lived in Jianghong Community, Area 3,
Building 3, Unit 2, Room 201.

38
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:43,320
Where did he live fifteen years ago?

39
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,480
How do you know that?

40
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:45,800
Fifteen years ago, I...

41
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:51,920
