112
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:31,880
I mean,

113
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:33,520
you have sharp eyes.

114
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,600
And a broad vision.

115
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:36,760
You'll definitely be the next principal.

116
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:44,600
You're too young to talk nonsense.

117
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,320
That's not your concern.

118
00:06:46,520 --> 00:06:47,880
You're in your final year now.

119
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:51,040
