128
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,040
Director.

129
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,800
I didn't throw trash in the cleaning area.

130
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:14,160
You didn't throw trash in the cleaning area,

131
