149
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,520
What are you whispering about?

150
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:22,720
Come on

151
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:24,680
Want some? I'll share half.

152
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:25,560
No, thanks.

153
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,240
