157
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:56,320
Don't take it to heart.

158
00:08:56,880 --> 00:08:59,000
They'll forget about it soon.

159
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:00,040
It's fine with me.

160
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:02,480
It's not a big deal anyway.

161
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,240
