166
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,800
I think there is.

167
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,520
What's the problem?

168
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:27,080
You think Su Ruo isn't

169
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:29,760
